<A>__{exley helps pull loew back inside. bud dumps him on the floor. bruised and bloodied, loew looks up at exley.}
<C>__{loew}
<D>__{dudley's got everyone under his thumb. not just me, but the chief of police, the lieutenant governor, everybody!}
<A>__{exley pulls his .38, shoves it into the side of loew's neck.}
<D>__{exley not everybody . you tip off dudley and officer white visits you alone next time.}
